  "contents": "\n\n<article>\n  <div class=\"page-actions\">\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L181-L201\" aria-label=\"Suggest Edits\" title=\"Suggest Edits\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">mode_edit</i></a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts#L181-L201\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n    <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n      {\n        \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n        \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n        \"itemListElement\": [\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io//api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common\", \"name\": \"@angular/common\" } },\n          { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/common/formatNumber\", \"name\": \"formatNumber\" } }\n        ]\n      }\n    </script>\n      <a href=\"/api\">API</a> / <a href=\"api/common\">@angular/common</a>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"formatnumber\">formatNumber<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatNumber#formatnumber\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label function\">function</label>\n    \n    \n    <label class=\"api-status-label stable\">stable</label>\n    \n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n    \n  <p class=\"short-description\"></p><p translation-origin=\"off\">Formats a number as text. Group sizing and separator and other locale-specific\nconfigurations are based on the locale.</p>\n<p></p>\n  \n  \n  \n\n  <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\"> <a href=\"api/common/formatNumber\" class=\"code-anchor\">formatNumber</a>(value: number, locale: string, digitsInfo?: string): string</code-example>\n\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"parameters\">Parameters</h4>\n<table class=\"is-full-width list-table parameters-table function-overload-parameters\">\n  <tbody>\n  \n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>value</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>number</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>locale</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr class=\"function-overload-parameter\">\n      <td class=\"param-name\"><a id=\"\"></a>digitsInfo</td>\n      \n      <td class=\"param-description\">\n            <p translation-origin=\"off\">Type: <code>string</code>.</p>\n      <p translation-origin=\"off\">Optional. Default is <code>undefined</code>.</p>\n      \n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n\n\n<h4 class=\"no-anchor\" id=\"returns\">Returns</h4>\n<p translation-origin=\"off\"><code>string</code></p>\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n  \n\n  \n\n<section class=\"description\">\n  <h2 id=\"description\">Description<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/common/formatNumber#description\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p translation-origin=\"off\">Where:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><code>value</code> is a number.</li>\n<li><code>locale</code> is a <code>string</code> defining the locale to use.</li>\n<li><code>digitInfo</code> See <a href=\"api/common/DecimalPipe\"><code>DecimalPipe</code></a> for more details.</li>\n</ul>\n\n</section>\n\n\n\n  \n\n\n  </div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/common\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/common\n - api/common/DecimalPipe\n - api/common/formatNumber#description\n - api/common/formatNumber#formatnumber\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/edit/master/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts?message=docs(common)%3A%20describe%20your%20change...#L181-L201\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/6.0.0/packages/common/src/i18n/format_number.ts#L181-L201\n-->"
